race.comment: ZIPPING SANDCHEZ (4) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won two of four starts. Missed the frame latest (26.29) when sixth over 460m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Expected to be in the finish. COOKIE MAN (1) goes very well this trip starting 15 times for seven wins and five minors. Placed last time (23.77) at Bendigo in a Special conditions H, finishing third and beaten 2.75 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. DISHEVELED (2) filled a minor placing last start at The Meadows behind Highly Connected (30.40) in a Mix 3/4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Must be included in calculations. KEEP ROLLING (3) must be included in calculations.
